When asked to create a new action, ask or deduct the <name> and optionally the <package> (assume <package> = <name> if not specified) then use:

  ops ai new <function> [<package>]

It will create the files:

- packages/<package>/<function>/__main__.py
- packages/<package>/<function>/<function>.py
- tests/<package>/test_<function>.py
- tests/<package>/test_<function>_int.py

When requested to create a tool, a resource or a prompt  ask or deduct the <name> and optionally the <package> (assume <package> = <name> if not specified). 

Then use:

  ops a41 new <package> <description> (--prompt=<name>|--tool=<name>|--resource=<name>)

It will generate the files:

- packages/<package>/<name>/__main__.py
- packages/<package>/<name>/<name>.py
- tests/<package>/test_<name>.py


